title.rendered: WSP Consultants India Pvt. Ltd. collaborates with Smile Foundation for Children’s Education

content.rendered:
WSP Consultants India Pvt. Ltd. collaborates with Smile Foundation for Children's Education

With focus on the continued education of children, Smile Foundation, in association with WSP Consultants India Private Limited is providing education to 400 children living in the underprivileged communities of Uttar Pradesh and Karnataka.
Other than regular classroom teaching learning, provision of digital learning, sanitation and hygiene, safe-drinking water and recreational facilities is also provided at the centres. In addition to these, creative classes of art, craft, music, dance, drama, etc. are also organized to bring out and enhance the hidden talent of the children to enable their holistic development.
We thank WSP Consultants India Private Limited for ensuring #ShikshaNaRuke for every child through Mission Education Centres – Noida Lok Manch and Sumangali Seva Ashrama in Gautam Buddha Nagar and RT Nagar districts of Uttar Pradesh and Karnataka respectively.
